metadata.name: God Save The People
metadata.description:
“No government is civilized till it abolishes all allegiance to the monarchy. Though monarchy and royalty are still considered a matter of pride in many uncivilized parts of the world, the day is not far when they'll be deemed a crime.”

Made in Adobe Photoshop | 7200x5400 @ 300dpi

Collector will receive a 50x70" print of the artwork + full-resolution files upon purchase.
